Have not visit Empress road market and food centre since Junior college days. Tried Mr Fun black pepper lamp chop. Food is nice.

However , many birds inside the food centre
I always have a good time ordering from this shop, portions are great, food is great. Price is also excellent ( $6.50 ) for a big chicken chop rice
Tried their Black Pepper Chicken Chop. Good amount of chicken, tender and flavourful, sauce also very good. Fries came out hot and crispy.  Reasonable price point for the quality
Chicken portion is big. Price is acceptable. One of the only few stalls that opens for dinner.

My regular dinner meal at empress market because only western food stalls are open. This is the best western food stall in empress market. Reasonable price and generous portion size. Had black pepper chicken chop  for this mealðŸ˜‹
